com.paypal.selion.internal.reports.model

Class PageContents

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.internal.reports.model.PageContents

  • public final class PageContents
extends Object
    Object representing web page contents. Internally used. PageContents will contain two aspects of a web page: 1.- The HTML page source
    2.- The rendered screen image of the page
    An ID string will be associated with each of the web page aspects. User can retrieved the page contents by using this ID.
